This project aims to show Rails3 simplicity and awesomeness by providing simple and small demos
within one application. Let's teach the newbies and inspire the best hackers.

Currently available demos: 
 * Dynamically removing some website content in Rails 3 Way (Prototype, UJS)


Feel free to fork, add demos and send pull requests.

Visit http://rails3demos.heroku.com/ for live application.
Visit http://github.com/paneq/rails3-demos to view the source code.
